research_municipality_step.notes: The Town of Rancho Viejo, TX operates under a General Law Type A government, which includes a Mayor and a Board of Aldermen. The terms for the elected officials vary, with some ending in May 2026 and others in May 2027. Non-elected administrative positions like Town Administrator, Town Attorney, Chief of Police, and Municipal Court Judge were excluded as per instructions.
